Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.51,0:00:12.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最喜欢这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.92,0:00:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为可以使用自己的双脚来走路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.88,0:00:42.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以巴斯血缘继承人的名义
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.37,0:00:45.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉醒吧 Aldnoah
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.30,0:02:33.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到你不仅仅活了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.28,0:02:37.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还肩负起了我国的指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.12,0:02:39.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太可靠了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.96,0:02:43.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以你为荣 亚瑟拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.78,0:02:46.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢您 爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.61,0:02:49.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许是我的心理作用 你好像变得坚强了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.98,0:02:51.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为发生了很多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.77,0:02:54.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们往往会在经验中发生改变吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.58,0:03:00.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲜红的大地 保佑你武运昌隆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.93,0:03:06.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你完全没变呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.03,0:03:12.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.86,0:03:17.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼叫三叉戟基地 我是Deucalion的马格巴丽吉舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.86,0:03:19.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请求入港
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.17,0:03:21.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎您的到来 Deucalion
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.79,0:03:23.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,批准你们的入港
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.02,0:03:26.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请停泊到12号码头
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.48,0:03:27.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Deucalion了解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.76,0:03:33.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路线设为三叉戟基地对接舱 在12号码头进行停泊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.76,0:03:33.57,ruby,NTP,0,45,0,,docking bay
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.13,0:03:35.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始减速
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.36,0:03:36.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始减速
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.81,0:03:42.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是利用火星的技术建造出来的战舰吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.62,0:03:45.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说预备役前的小孩子们也在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.32,0:03:48.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.33,0:03:51.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好庞大的战力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.56,0:03:55.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们一定将能召集到的部队都召集到这里了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.55,0:03:58.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这是一次大规模作战
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.74,0:04:00.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离减速完成还有5秒…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.19,0:04:04.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3 2 1！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.38,0:04:10.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两舷停止 已相对停止于12号码头
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.44,0:04:14.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全舰停止 系泊完成后立刻进行检查和补给
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:25.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,界冢少尉 你在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.27,0:04:27.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,门开着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.72,0:04:35.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,状态如何 伊奈帆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.40,0:04:38.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不错 虽然还有点疼就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.45,0:04:39.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,药呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.79,0:04:41.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然吃了药会感觉好一些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:43.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但吃药了会使神经链路的敏感度下降
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.62,0:04:45.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.21,0:04:47.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也挺不容易的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.41,0:04:56.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去和普通的眼睛没啥区别呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.95,0:04:58.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这东西很厉害吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.94,0:05:00.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勉勉强强凑合着用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.64,0:05:02.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是开发中的原型样板
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.68,0:05:04.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还得进一步改良程序
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.54,0:05:07.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过大多数东西都是可以辨认出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.10,0:05:08.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.49,0:05:11.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.05,0:05:14.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,体重 49.2公斤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.44,0:05:15.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你长胖了点？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.64,0:05:17.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你为什么会知道啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.22,0:05:23.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用三维测量计算了在你接住200g包裹时的动量变化
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.94,0:05:25.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从而计算出了你的总重量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.80,0:05:28.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此基础上减去了制服的重量就得出结果了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.84,0:05:30.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家才没有胖啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:32.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家只不过经过锻炼长肌肉了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.25,0:05:34.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是在说谎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.64,0:05:37.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过对你声音的共振峰分析能看出你很紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.64,0:05:37.41,ruby,NTP,0,100,0,,formant
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.55,0:05:39.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那东西不是坏了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.77,0:05:41.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常正常             
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.47,0:05:43.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.34,0:05:46.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也能从她的声音里听出同样的紧张感
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.93,0:05:47.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.52,0:05:52.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}我是巴斯帝国第一皇女 亚瑟拉姆·巴斯·艾莉欧西亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.40,0:05:54.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.74,0:05:56.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这台词是骗人的…那么这就意味着…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.36,0:05:58.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不是真正的公主？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.01,0:06:01.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然刚刚的波形是说谎了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.51,0:06:02.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,压力太大吃多了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.66,0:06:03.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃你妹！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.74,0:06:05.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紧张度又上升了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.98,0:06:08.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再也不和你说话了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.95,0:06:15.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.05,0:06:16.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.14,0:06:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是觉得韵子太容易读懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:24.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.16,0:06:28.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你其实是个笨蛋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.93,0:06:33.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有说谎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.17,0:06:43.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯雷因大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.80,0:06:47.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾德尔丽泽 你不用伺候雷姆蕾娜公主吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.45,0:06:52.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 我会替你保密的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.16,0:06:54.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.06,0:06:58.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 我找到了你之前跟我说的那艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:06:59.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是Deucalion吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.53,0:07:02.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那艘船好像暗中经过修理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.94,0:07:05.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说他们打倒雅克伊姆男爵后飞到宇宙来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.22,0:07:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有可能要跟他们战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.94,0:07:15.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟拉姆公主会伤心的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.57,0:07:19.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主殿下何时会醒过来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.06,0:07:22.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果她就这样一直不…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.72,0:07:24.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.70,0:07:28.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一定会再次看到她的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.08,0:07:30.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主殿下…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.34,0:07:51.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟拉姆就托付给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.37,0:07:55.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都已经安排好了 请您放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.61,0:07:57.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.09,0:08:10.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到之前谎称她已经被暗杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.87,0:08:13.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次却要谎称她还活着…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.15,0:08:16.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯雷因啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:18.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么看待现在的巴斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.83,0:08:21.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这种人怎敢对神圣的大地抱有意见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.95,0:08:24.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无所谓 尽管说出你的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:30.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有力量的市民为生活所困扰的社会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.12,0:08:35.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为通过攻击地球 将之纳入我国版图 获取资源
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:37.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以得到财富
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.39,0:08:39.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.67,0:08:40.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.34,0:08:45.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些财富很可能会流向上层阶级
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.72,0:08:48.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不会改善市民的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.89,0:08:50.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 你要怎么去做？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.18,0:08:53.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aldnoah…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.39,0:08:56.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得Aldnoah者掌控一切
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.79,0:09:00.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是一切问题的根源
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.73,0:09:02.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.66,0:09:06.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发掘出Aldnoah确实是皇帝陛下的丰功伟绩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.79,0:09:09.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他将此力量独占
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.14,0:09:13.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并建立起由有力量的人支配的社会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.59,0:09:15.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,则是一个很大的罪过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.95,0:09:19.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在赢得战争 支配地球之时
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.22,0:09:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们将改变那颗鲜红的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.10,0:09:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为我贡献你的力量 斯雷因
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.01,0:09:30.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 扎赫巴姆伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:36.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的爱骑准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.24,0:09:37.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,启动测试已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.11,0:09:42.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后只要完成各单元的同步调整就可以实战了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.34,0:09:43.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在岛上进行调整
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.27,0:09:46.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Stygis队 准备出击！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.36,0:09:46.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.47,0:09:55.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tharsis 启动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.32,0:09:59.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有启动？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.46,0:10:02.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aldnoah Drive停止了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.05,0:10:03.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.01,0:10:15.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷姆蕾娜公主
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.71,0:10:21.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出什么事了吗 斯雷因
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.89,0:10:24.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您为什么要停止Tharsis呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.61,0:10:26.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.32,0:10:31.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里只有公主殿下可以强制停止Aldnoah
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.88,0:10:33.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:39.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请启动Aldnoah
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.52,0:10:41.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.52,0:10:42.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.51,0:10:45.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去拜托皇姐如何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.18,0:10:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前我就觉得很不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.24,0:10:52.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到底你一个地球人 为何能驱动Tharsis
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.22,0:10:55.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来皇姐也相当幸福呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.84,0:10:59.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都变成这副惨样了还有人深爱着她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.93,0:11:03.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明父亲都是同一个人 仅仅因为母亲有别
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.10,0:11:06.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就没任何人来理会我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.85,0:11:08.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.61,0:11:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都很仰慕雷姆蕾娜公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.99,0:11:12.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.72,0:11:13.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有骗您
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.91,0:11:14.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是在骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.08,0:11:17.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们所仰慕的不是我 而是我的启动因子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.43,0:11:20.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你才来到这里的不是么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.66,0:11:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯雷因大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.30,0:11:26.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这么想要我的帮助？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.86,0:11:28.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aldnoah对你就如此重要？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.01,0:11:33.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是皇姐的代替品？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.11,0:11:38.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊…果然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.74,0:11:42.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我讨厌你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.08,0:11:53.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出生于地球
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.88,0:11:55.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当身为科学家的父亲去世后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.83,0:11:57.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去了依靠的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.21,0:12:01.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为了巴斯轨道骑士的仆人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.12,0:12:12.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会说我完全理解公主殿下您的艰辛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:16.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…我也是因出身而受苦之人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.12,0:12:20.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以您的苦恼 我想我还是理解一些的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.35,0:12:28.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我由衷仰慕你 我主雷姆蕾娜公主
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.70,0:12:32.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抬起头来 斯雷因
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.99,0:12:40.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就能启动一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.26,0:12:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己去做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.55,0:12:45.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.93,0:12:50.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝您好运 斯雷因·托罗亚特骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.74,0:12:57.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯雷因大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.74,0:12:59.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.16,0:13:01.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很佩服你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.58,0:13:04.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能为您效劳 我非常光荣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.31,0:13:05.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.95,0:13:06.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见笑了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.63,0:13:11.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全机发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.35,0:13:14.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标 马里内罗岛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.35,0:13:14.31,ruby,NTP,75,0,0,,Marineros
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.69,0:13:27.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所拥有的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.16,0:13:30.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都由我来继承吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.64,0:13:35.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 您就放心吧 皇姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.17,0:13:50.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们即将进入地球自转轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.12,0:13:56.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用航空制动 之后上升脱离 最后突入卫星带
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.70,0:13:58.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后前往马里内罗岛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.99,0:14:00.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯雷因大人 差不多是时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.96,0:14:01.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.00,0:14:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.11,0:14:46.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漂浮在卫星带里的无数的岩石
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.05,0:14:49.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正以地球为中心作椭圆轨道运动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.26,0:14:52.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们三叉戟基地也是那些岩石中的一个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.95,0:14:57.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而火星军的前线基地马里内罗轨道便是这条
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.96,0:15:01.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两者在72小时后到达最近点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.86,0:15:04.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其距离只有短短的7公里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.25,0:15:05.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是敌我双方可以肉眼目视彼此的距离
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.97,0:15:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从而推测两基地间可能会因此发生大规模的攻防战
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.12,0:15:17.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对此 我让轨道上以及地面上拥有强大战力的诸位集结到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.73,0:15:21.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们认为火星军也将聚集他们的全部力量发起总攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.11,0:15:24.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在座的各位请不要掉以轻心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.76,0:15:25.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来我进行作战说明
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.02,0:15:30.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自从开战以来 我们从来就没有打过如此大规模的宇宙战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.83,0:15:31.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.30,0:15:33.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.04,0:15:38.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是只要想想敌人也是第一次就没什么可怕的了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.96,0:15:42.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…我仍然感到不安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.57,0:15:44.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.72,0:15:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.71,0:15:48.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你这可爱的一面也在日常中展现的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.02,0:15:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该会多一点桃花运吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.31,0:15:54.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离减速结束还有5秒…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.81,0:15:58.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3 2 1
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.20,0:15:59.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脱离
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.93,0:16:08.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺手给敌人一点见面礼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.74,0:16:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Stygis队啊 为我展示你们的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.13,0:16:14.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Stygis-1 谨遵上令
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.44,0:16:22.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Stygis-2 谨遵上令
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.24,0:16:27.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Stygis-3 谨遵上令
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.38,0:16:46.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高热源体正从近地轨道方向急速接近这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.55,0:16:48.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌我识别信号没有应答
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.00,0:16:50.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然从下面来？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.30,0:16:52.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对方正高速通过距离本基地2km的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.25,0:16:56.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,取的是前往火星军马里内罗基地的轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.38,0:16:58.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司令部发来了迎击命令
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.12,0:17:03.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高速接近的中型船只7艘 以及3个小型机机影
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.03,0:17:06.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们打算在总攻开始之前发动突袭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.55,0:17:08.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可行动的全部舰载机出击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.10,0:17:10.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本舰也做好紧急发射的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.45,0:17:14.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡姆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.09,0:17:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的机体如何了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.26,0:17:17.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经完成了修理
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.59,0:17:19.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙装备也更换好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.02,0:17:20.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.04,0:17:23.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过真要用这么显眼的颜色吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.06,0:17:25.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是发话 我就帮你换个色
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.24,0:17:27.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了 这算是一个标志
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.72,0:17:28.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.83,0:17:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.39,0:17:45.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ghanaati小队 配置结束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.68,0:17:48.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Harroway小队 配置结束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.26,0:17:53.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mustang-11 配置结束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:55.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mustang-22 配置结束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.14,0:17:59.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与敌机的相对速度为每秒3公里左右
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.36,0:18:00.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们会在一瞬间擦肩而过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.83,0:18:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这意味着攻击的时机仅有一瞬间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.32,0:18:07.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Stygis-1 开始攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.14,0:18:15.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Stygis-2 开始攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.91,0:18:19.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Stygis-3 开始攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.44,0:18:24.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对方开始攻击了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.72,0:18:28.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.75,0:18:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风向太过复杂了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.16,0:18:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌我双方以目前这个距离都很难打中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.15,0:18:51.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打中了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.11,0:18:52.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个距离？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.71,0:18:58.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mustang-00 开始攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.55,0:18:59.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊奈帆！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.07,0:19:02.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高密度卫星群所产生的重力梯度
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.86,0:19:03.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,数据补正完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.41,0:19:05.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标设定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.89,0:19:07.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.53,0:19:12.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.31,0:19:15.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.23,0:19:19.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Stygis队被…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.59,0:19:22.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊奈帆！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.03,0:19:36.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧 伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.68,0:19:37.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯雷因
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.54,0:19:39.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己来当诱饵来吸引对方的火力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.23,0:19:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈库莱特先生 请采取回避运动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.28,0:19:43.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.93,0:19:53.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会被打中！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.31,0:19:56.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躲开了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.51,0:20:09.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很敏捷的动作…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.11,0:20:11.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正确无比的射击！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.99,0:20:13.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然能这种乱风中打中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.10,0:20:21.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,速度？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.94,0:20:22.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.28,0:20:24.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对方看清了子弹的轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.63,0:20:26.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.56,0:20:27.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是怎样的敌人？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.63,0:20:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.92,0:20:35.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,橙色的机体…!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.68,0:20:36.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.03,0:20:39.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找你好久了 蝙蝠…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.72,0:20:42.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 现在变成海鸥了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.90,0:20:54.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌舰团即将进入有效射程
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.65,0:20:56.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自由攻击！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.99,0:21:04.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊奈帆！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.16,0:21:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌舰团通过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.58,0:21:22.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正驶离本区域
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.89,0:21:25.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续射击 直到敌人超出射程
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.62,0:21:26.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,报告受损情况！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.13,0:21:31.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tharsis…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.71,0:21:35.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本是轨道骑士库鲁迪欧伯爵所有的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.09,0:21:40.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后为扎赫巴姆伯爵所有并配给了其麾下的骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.40,0:21:42.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搭乘者的名字是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.71,0:21:44.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,橙色的机体…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.59,0:21:46.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是练习机
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.30,0:21:48.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,练习机？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.43,0:21:51.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人就爱开练习机
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.06,0:21:52.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.07,0:21:56.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…他的名字是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.61,0:21:58.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,界冢伊奈帆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.51,0:22:00.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来你还活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.08,0:22:01.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.86,0:22:04.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯雷因·托罗亚特
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.97,0:22:10.97,title,NTP,0,0,0,,“异星的邻人”
